T1  - Pension fund equity performance: Patience, activity or both?
AU  - Artiga González, Tanja
AU  - van Lelyveld, Iman
AU  - Lučivjanská, Katarína
JO  - Journal of Banking & Finance
VL  - 115
SP  - 105812
